Package dev.project276.entity

Class Door

java.lang.Object
dev.project276.entity.Entity
dev.project276.entity.Door
Direct Known Subclasses:
Exit
public class Door
extends Entity
The Door entity. The Player must have a key to be able to pass through a Door. If they do, the key is used up and the Door is in an open state, and can be walked through.
